{"tid":703903,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【義犬救爸】被出賣食夾棍母患癌 可憐仁第二次自殺","createTime":"2018-06-16T04:19:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-16T09:08:44.000Z","uid":22675,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e284e975f21fb49021d5d4f38d728233e62ee65a","tid":703903,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T04:19:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kgBADk5tedI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DkgBADk5tedI&d=bTxF3GTHIY4ejja7HVfaoTCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=62e368fe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kgBADk5tedI</a><br />\n「可憐仁」陳達仁有鋪癮收徒弟，徒弟都有鋪癮出賣他，徒弟2.0出賣他兼頂爛市搶生意，他欠下巨債，選擇自殺2.0，打算從48樓一躍而下。（他還要死幾多次？）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n話說某年春節後人人開市，只有喃嘸佬陳達仁門庭冷落，少人過身固然是好，然而天國與地獄接收的移民卻沒稍減。阿仁問徒弟發生何事，對方卻一口請辭。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n教識徒弟無師父不算什麼，最怕養狗咬代代相傳的殯儀行業，有個殯儀行街先生－－即是殯儀sales－－向他爆料，原來那徒弟找上很多行街先生，都是阿仁熟客，以低廉價錢及紅酒雪茄等禮物搶客，過往陳生的拿手好戲，徒弟學個十足，用來回饋師父，致他死命，師父請安息吧！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n可憐仁再回頭失去八成生意，帳簿上欠債卻有百多二百萬，紙紮、祭品等供應商等着要錢。一不離二，當日他將生意交給徒兒，自己雄圖偉略開棺材鋪，可惜努力不等於回報，早起鳥兒有蟲吃，早起蟲兒被鳥吃，當時他仍是蟲仔，不懂法律程序，被生意伙伴吃掉股份。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n二不離三，媽媽這時證實患上肺癌，標靶藥及補品每月盛惠幾萬塊錢。阿仁一次過滿足三個願望，只好低頭向親戚借錢，對方認為如此奇情只在粵語片及出奇蛋發生，要他出示醫生紙。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n當時他不自知抑鬱，每天眼淚當潔面乳液，電話響當作聽不見，面對電視節目當作看見，其實眼前只有死字，死後不用還債，保險賠償也足夠讓媽媽治病。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n他輕撫伏在腿上的愛犬，自怨自艾：「爸爸沒錢養你！」一天不知哪裡來的膽子，踏上窗台，樓高48層，沒有窗花，只要窗口當門口，表演一次空中飛人，所有難關不是難關。愛犬見他動作有異，不住吠叫，媽媽聞聲跑出，拉他下來。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n時至今日，陳達仁救狗成名，因為狗救過他；時至今日，他發現遇上多大難關也不用死，幾多好戲都在後頭，可惜媽媽見不着。"},{"pid":"578210bb55536940d0a23ca1de3d5ca8090e1eb2","tid":703903,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T04:19:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://nextplus.nextmedia.com/news/spot/20180616/594491\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnextplus.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fspot%2F20180616%2F594491&d=bTxF3GTHIY4ejja7HVfaoTCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=4fed1fbb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnextplus.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fspot%2F20180616%2F594491&h=8ec73b09\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://nextplus.nextmedia.com/news/spot/20180616/594491</a>"},{"pid":"8b8c0251f8332a48349a29e61d01029cfe9f5973","tid":703903,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T04:41:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62bdfe4232b5634b2574a813e8b5b5e6709bf49b","tid":703903,"uid":4575,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T04:45:03.000Z","msg":"春乜撚野節，邊度新聞"},{"pid":"f8944c68c2cfdf0253f52d674d700780e5984994","tid":703903,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T04:53:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=MBf8B6sX2Fg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DMBf8B6sX2Fg&d=bTxF3GTHIY4ejja7HVfaoTCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=3c9fe16d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=MBf8B6sX2Fg</a>"},{"pid":"86a0eb0cdaf3452afc50e7efcee71d421bbc86da","tid":703903,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T05:02:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e612374336db9231f80f90413d2a2f14779c1a0f","tid":703903,"uid":73052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T05:08:40.000Z","msg":"點法律程序法 可以食哂股份？"},{"pid":"feb283349ab47dfc9167c3a2d08a2639d9cb7705","tid":703903,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T06:49:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfe47ee3e470d49f2325dead0985e6990f22a3a4","tid":703903,"uid":99978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T07:13:07.000Z","msg":"佢當初點搶人生意<br />\n人地咪搶返佢<br />\n講到好可憐咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c26fca2b712e770bfb6ea1bbdd54417118595099","